			<h2>Terms of Sale</h2>
				<p>Tickets will be on general sale through Eventbrite from 10am on April 25th 2013. A limited amount of earlybird tickets will be released first at the price of &pound;49. Once these are sold out, standard tickets will go on sale at &pound;69. </p>

